metadata.dc:author: Acevedo, P
metadata.dc:description: Cheyletiella parasitovorax, Haemodipsus sp. and Listrophorus sp. are described in 137 rabbits from Juan Fernández Islands examined during 1989. The occurrence of Haemodipsus sp. and Listrophorus sp. represents two new parasite records for Chile.
metadata.dc:title: Ectoparásitos de conejos silvestres (Oryctolagus cuniculus) del Archipiélago de Juan Fernández.
[Ectoparasites of wild rabbits (Oryctolagus cuniculus) from the Juan Fernández archipelago].
